{"tid":1973809,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"孫兒因買錯矮瓜被毆打","createTime":"2020-04-15T12:04:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T17:59:55.000Z","uid":60658,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"63fcc1cf493fe46121e5594efaa9bbb85b40c897","tid":1973809,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T12:04:03.000Z","msg":"根據調查，阿嫲和孫兒（20歲）約好，要孫兒替他購買矮瓜。不過從早上就去排隊的孫兒，卻買回了別的青瓜，這讓阿嫲相當惱火。在吃晚飯時，阿嫲拿起放在餐桌上的水果刀旁邊的青瓜（長30厘米），不斷毆打孫兒。<br />\n<br />\n聽到孫兒的慘叫的父親急忙來阻止了阿嫲，不過孫兒的額頭還是受了輕微的毆傷。阿嫲被附近接到報告的警察逮捕。在調查中阿嫲供訴到：「一想到他那麼早出去到底去排了什麼一X一，就惱火的不得了。」<br />\n<br />\n警視廳表示，今後類似這種由於親子間對買餸的理解溝通不充分，而引發的暴力事件，還將有可能發生，請大家引以為戒。"},{"pid":"412d10ccb603e0a849e4d32f2b50e85b434e4468","tid":1973809,"uid":141999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T12:04:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2da7749e312e54dc9311c5a4ab1a71d25a8d280e","tid":1973809,"uid":13106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T12:05:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bcf7359b729ca508e9c028f0582c0276216be22","tid":1973809,"uid":189109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T12:05:06.000Z","msg":"以為有新潮文 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74653ce96abc33a9007a5d535f651fc72af4fd72","tid":1973809,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bcf7359b729ca508e9c028f0582c0276216be22","tid":1973809,"uid":189109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T12:05:06.000Z","msg":"以為有新潮文 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T12:05:29.000Z","msg":"呢篇都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb857d4c492c172be20b1a84c4ef6cb26840572d","tid":1973809,"uid":82482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite